source.name: Pedestrian Fatalities and Severe Injuries from Vehicle-Pedestrian Collisions (2005 to 2010) - San Francisco, CA
source.description: Vehicle collisions resulting in a severe pedestrian injury or fatality. Reported through the California Highway Patrol, Statewide Integrated Traffic Reporting System (SWITRS) between 2005 to 2010. Geocoded to the nearest intersection.
